---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Contact Us"
description: "Get a free flooring estimate from Best Practice Flooring LLC. Call Ake at (503) 884-1711 or fill out our contact form. Serving Corvallis, Independence & the Mid-Willamette Valley."
permalink: /contact/
---

<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Contact Best Practice Flooring</h1>
  <p>Get your free, no-obligation estimate. We'd love to hear about your project.</p>
</div>

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));gap:var(--space-3xl);align-items:start;">

      {# Contact Form #}
      <div>
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-xl);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);color:var(--text-primary);">Request a Free Estimate</h2>
        <form class="contact-form" action="mailto:bestpracticeflooringllc@gmail.com" method="POST" enctype="text/plain" style="max-width:none;">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name" class="form-label">Your Name <span class="form-required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="form-input" required autocomplete="name" placeholder="Your full name">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone" class="form-label">Phone Number <span class="form-required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" class="form-input" required autocomplete="tel" placeholder="(503) 555-1234">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-input" autocomplete="email">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="service" class="form-label">Service Interested In</label>
            <select id="service" name="service" class="form-select">
              <option value="">Select a service...</option>
              {% for svc in site.services %}
              <option value="{{ svc.name }}">{{ svc.name }}</option>
              {% endfor %}
              <option value="Other">Other / Not Sure</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message" class="form-label">Tell Us About Your Project</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" class="form-textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Room size, current flooring, what you're looking for..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%;">Get My Free Estimate</button>
          <p style="margin-top:var(--space-sm);font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--text-muted);text-align:center;">We typically respond within a few hours during business hours.</p>
        </form>
      </div>

      {# Contact Info #}
      <div>
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-xl);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);color:var(--text-primary);">Reach Us Directly</h2>

        <div style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2xl);">
          <h3 style="font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:var(--space-sm);">Ake — Owner &amp; Installer</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);">
            <a href="tel:+1{{ site.team.ake.phone }}" style="color:var(--brand-primary);font-weight:600;font-size:var(--text-lg);text-decoration:none;">{{ site.team.ake.phoneDisplay }}</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2xl);">
          <h3 style="font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:var(--space-sm);">Sarah — Scheduling &amp; Coordination</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);">
            <a href="tel:+1{{ site.team.sarah.phone }}" style="color:var(--brand-primary);font-weight:600;font-size:var(--text-lg);text-decoration:none;">{{ site.team.sarah.phoneDisplay }}</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2xl);">
          <h3 style="font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:var(--space-sm);">Email</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);">
            <a href="mailto:bestpracticeflooringllc@gmail.com" style="color:var(--brand-primary);font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">bestpracticeflooringllc@gmail.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2xl);">
          <h3 style="font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:var(--space-sm);">Business Hours</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;">
            <strong>Monday – Friday:</strong> {{ site.hours.weekdays }}<br>
            <strong>Saturday:</strong> {{ site.hours.saturday }}<br>
            <strong>Sunday:</strong> {{ site.hours.sunday }}
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2xl);">
          <h3 style="font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:var(--space-sm);">Service Area</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;">Based in Independence, OR. We serve Corvallis, Salem, Albany, Monmouth, Dallas, Philomath, and the entire Mid-Willamette Valley.</p>
          <a href="/service-areas/" style="color:var(--brand-primary);font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">View all service areas →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <h2>We Respond Fast</h2>
  <p>Most inquiries get a response within a few hours. Call us directly for the quickest answer, or use the form above and we'll get back to you promptly.</p>
  <div class="cta-buttons">
    <a href="tel:+1{{ site.team.ake.phone }}" class="btn btn-primary" style="background:#fff;color:var(--brand-primary);">Call Ake: {{ site.team.ake.phoneDisplay }}</a>
    <a href="tel:+1{{ site.team.sarah.phone }}" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Sarah: {{ site.team.sarah.phoneDisplay }}</a>
  </div>
</section>
